                                                      <h6>6. Disclosure of your information</h6>
                                                      <p>
                                                          We will not usually disclose your personal data other than as already explained in sections 3 and 5 above. However, there may be circumstances where we need to share personal data other than as anticipated in sections 3 and 5 above. These include:
                                                      </p> <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                                      <ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;">
                                                          <li>where we are legally required to disclose the information. This includes sharing the personal data with tax authorities and law enforcement agencies for the purposes of the prevention and detection of crime;</li>
